  "title": "🦅 Field Marketing – On-the-Go, On-the-Rise 🌍📈",
  "description": "<p>Are you pumped about marketing, creativity, and real-world experience? Love meeting new people and making ideas happen? Come grow with us  an energetic team helping top brands connect with audiences and build unforgettable stories! </p><h3>🔥 Why You’ll Love This Role</h3><p>✨ <strong>Hands-on experience from Day 1</strong> — work on live campaigns, and events<br />💡 <strong>Full training + mentorship</strong> — we’ll help you build real skills, no experience needed<br />📈 <strong>Clear growth path</strong> — performance matters — promotions and bigger roles await<br />🤝 <strong>Team culture</strong> — supportive, collaborative, fun environment<br />🌍 <strong>Exciting opportunities</strong> — travel, network, and learn beyond the desk<br />💬 <strong>Boost your confidence & communications skills</strong> every day </p><h3>🚀 What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li>Represent brands at campaigns, events, and activations</li><li>Engage with audiences and customers</li><li>Support team projects and help launch marketing activities</li><li>Bring fresh ideas and energy to the table</li><li>Learn fast and build valuable skills step by step </li></ul><h3>🧠 Who We Think Will Thrive</h3><p>This role is perfect for you if you:<br />✔️ Are curious, eager to learn, and ready for new challenges<br />✔️ Enjoy talking with people and being part of a dynamic team<br />✔️ Want real experience — not just another desk job<br />✔️ Are excited to grow a career in marketing and communications</p><p><em>(Fresh graduates, post-ORD, or early career switchers are all welcome — no strict experience requirements.)</em> </p>",
